snippet.title: Fist of the Forgotten WIP Gameplay Trailer 2
snippet.description:
https://fistoftheforgotten.com/ - Add the game to your wishlist and sign up for the mailing list to get updates and possibly get into the beta.


FOTF is still heavily in development, but here's a trailer to show off some of the gameplay and environments so far!


#indiegame #platformer #GodotEngine
